    description: "Concatenated set of certificates in PEM format"
    default: ""
    example: |
      -----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----
      MIIClTCCAf4CCQDc6hJtvGB8RjANBgkqhkiG9w0BAQUFADCBjjELMAk...
      -----END CERTIFICATE-----
      -----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----
      MIIClTCCAf4CCQDc6hJtvGB8RjANBgkqhkiG9w0BAQUFADCBjjELMAk...
      -----END CERTIFICATE-----
